videos.description: On the fast break, Baylor's King McClure feeds Jo Lual-Acuil Jr. for a dunk early against Oklahoma.
videos.headline: McClure sets up Lual-Acuil Jr. for dunk

videos.description: Oklahoma's Khadeem Lattin gets a block on Baylor's Johnathan Motley.
videos.headline: Lattin gets up to reject Motley's shot

videos.description: Baylor's Jake Lindsey gets a steal and Nuni Omot then assists on a Johnathan Motley dunk.
videos.headline: Baylor steal leads to a Motley dunk
